Localization.Name: Klaus & Werner
Localization.Description: Formed in 2893, Klaus & Werner makes guns, and they make them well. This simple philosophy was the brainchild of Hector Klaus, a successful weapons inventor who believed above all else that simplicity of design would triumph in a combat situation.

Localization.Name: Fresnel "Rockfall" Energy LMG
Localization.Description:
Manufacturer: Verified Offworld Laser Technologies
Item Type: LMG
Class: Energy (Electron)

Battery Size: 165
Rate of Fire: 550 rpm - 220 rpm
Effective Range: 50m

Attachments: Optics (S3), Underbarrel (S3)

The engineers at VOLT crafted the Fresnel LMG to bring a powerful energy weapon to the frontlines, one that can initiate a fight with a rapid spray of deadly blasts. As the weapon heats up, the shots become slower and more powerful, but be careful of overheating. A weapon of this magnitude demands a strong foundation; operators are encouraged to fire from a crouching position to allow for better recoil management.

The Rockfall edition showcases a rugged green with natural accents.
